DSLJSONYAML <p>Without a label:</p> <pre><code>Start:
</code></pre> <p>Without a label:</p> <pre><code>Start: my label
</code></pre> <p>Without a label:</p> <pre><code>{
"element": "Start"
}
</code></pre> <p>With a label:</p> <pre><code>{
"element": "Start",
"label": "my label"
}
</code></pre> <p>With the sql type:</p> <pre><code>{
"element": "Start",
"type": "sql"
}
</code></pre> <p>Without a label:</p> <pre><code>element: Start
</code></pre> <p>With a label</p> <pre><code>element: Start
label: my label
</code></pre> <p>With the sql type:</p> <pre><code>element: Start
